h 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP, though Super-Mods may deploy their 500 PX initial treasury to incentivize urgent troubleshooting. By hosting this operational crisis management locally on an NVIDIA Jetson, the community maintains absolute data sovereignty, ensuring its internal vulnerabilities are never exposed to centralized cloud trackers. This archived memory is vital for future generations, like those in the 70 ETS Student Clubs, to understand how to maintain system throughput under pressure. Once resolved, this memo becomes a cryptographic seed for Phase 3: The Awakening. ROM, the local RAG engine, will digest this history to provide predictive warnings and automated flow management in the future. Documenting ''Embouteillage Ops'' at D9 transforms a moment of operational failure into a permanent asset of organizational intelligence, securing the node''s long-term survival for the decade ahead. This entry establishes the essential baseline for system resilience, ensuring that our collective memory remains safe from the entropy of internal operational friction. Yes.', 'This quest addresses critical operational bottlenecks at coordinate D9, using the Guardian role to resolve systemic friction and archiving the solutions as sovereign deep lore.');
