vital for encouraging high-quality participation and ensuring the community reaches the 100-memo goal required to unlock Phase 2. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, E3 is the coordinate where the club''s specific cultural and technical legacy is first formally documented, ensuring that knowledge transfer remains consistent across student generations. Once the node reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, these ''Chantier Piliers'' memos will be among the primary documents ingested by ROM, the local RAG engine. Ultimately, E3 transforms the node''s thematic vision into a tangible, permanent structural reality. Every brick laid here is a step toward the survival of human memory. This archived work ensures that the community''s intent remains clear as it navigates toward the global lobby. The construction of our shared memory is a sacred duty for all. This finalized record at coordinate E3 acts as the definitive anchor for our shared culture. Mission secure. Our journey is now complete. Yes.', 'This quest establishes the formal construction site for thematic pillars at coordinate E3, transforming vision into actionable, archived content for the node''s long-term memory.');
