t rewards the contributor with 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP, facilitating the healthy flow of value within the node. This incentive structure is vital for encouraging the ''Social'' role (Blue alignment) and ''Creators'' to design the financial tools that will secure the collective future. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, G0 ensures that the internal economy is tailored to the specific needs of student organizations, providing a template for future generations to manage their own resources. Once the node reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, these economic ideas will be ingested by ROM, the local RAG engine, allowing the AI to assist in balancing the Pixel economy based on original intent. Ultimately, G0 transforms abstract financial needs into a structured, actionable vision that secures the node''s economic integrity. This entry is now canonized for the decade. Yes. Our money is our sovereignty. Perfect. Done. Mission secure. This systematic planning at coordinate G0 ensures that every subsequent transaction remains perfectly aligned. Now.', 'This quest initiates the conceptualization of the node''s internal economy at coordinate G0, establishing the monetary logic required for the forom''s long-term digital sovereignty.');
