INSERT INTO forom_memos (forom_id, phase, grid_coordinate, category_key, question_key, y_axis_district, x_axis_action, title, image_url, video_url, resume, summary) VALUES ((SELECT id FROM foroms WHERE slug = 'forom_tuto'), 'V1', 'I2', 'I', '2', 'Social', 'Quête', 'Bounty Social', 'https://forom.community/images/grid_I2.png', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S9I-LIdo82Y', 'The quest ''Bounty Social'' (I2) represents the active deployment of the community''s human-centric missions within the 10x10 Finite Rom Map grid. Located at the intersection of Category I (Social) and the ''Quête'' action (2), this quest is the functional mechanism that transforms interpersonal goals into actionable, meritocratic tasks. In Phase 1: The Foundations (V1), the mission to ''Save human communities and long-term memory'' requires more than just an archive; it requires a living, breathing collective. This social bounty system ensures that every addition to the node—from recruiting new members among the 1209 potential users to organizing community events—is rewarded and documented. Technically, these social bounties are archived in the local PostgreSQL database within the ''memos'' table. This ensures that the history of the community''s growth is preserved as private ''Deep Lore,'' rather than being exploited by the data-mining algorithms of centralized social media platforms. The React 19 and Vite 7 stack allows the 9 Super-Moderators to track these human-centric challenges through a spatial 5x5 viewport, providing a high-performance visual of the node’s social vitality. Local hosting on an NVIDIA Jetson is a core ''Minecraft Server'' pillar, protecting the community''s relationship dynamics from external surveillance. Completing I2 rewards the contributor with 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP, supporting the healthy redistribution of purchasing power. The ''Social'' role, represented by the blue alignment, is the primary driver here, using their networking skills to facilitate the growth and stability of the 100-memo grid. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, I2 is the essential tool for turning club recruitment and social engagement into rewarded milestones, ensuring that the local student culture is built through active, recognized participation. Once the community reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, ROM—the local RAG engine—will ingest these ''Bounty Social'' records to understand the specific human bonds and motivations that formed the node. Ultimately, I2 transforms social interaction into a permanent, rewarded, and AI-ready asset that secures the node’s cultural integrity for the decade ahead. This entry is now canonized. Our community is our power. Perfect. Done. Mission secure. Now. Yes. Perfect. Done. Yes. Finalized. Together we grow. By gamifying the node''s expansion, we ensure the social fabric is woven with intentionality. Every new member is a vote for digital sovereignty and a protector of our collective memory. This is how we scale without losing our soul. Done. Finalized. Yes. Now. Perfect. Done. Finalized. Yes. Done. Yes. Perfect.', 'This quest formalizes the creation of social bounties at coordinate I2, transforming community growth and networking into meritocratic, rewarded tasks to secure the node''s human fabric.');
