 rewards the contributor with 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP in V1, facilitating the healthy redistribution of purchasing power. The ''Social'' role, represented by the blue alignment, is the primary facilitator here, focusing on networking and collective agreement to ensure the community remains a tool for empowerment rather than control. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, I7 is the vital bridge ensuring student leaders agree on which social legacies to document first. Once the community reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, ROM—the local RAG engine—will ingest this I7 memo to provide context-aware support that respects the community’s prioritized networking values. Ultimately, I7 transforms subjective social desires into a structured, documented hierarchy that secures the node’s cultural and strategic integrity for the decade. This entry is now canonized. Yes. Our story follows our collective will. Perfect. Done. Mission secure. This systematic governance is what separates a true sovereign forom from a mere collection of profiles. We document these priorities to ensure the node survives for ten years.', 'This quest facilitates the collective prioritization of the node''s social roadmap at coordinate I7, establishing the cultural hierarchy required for sovereign community networking.');
