rom the algorithmic manipulation common in centralized social media. Economically, participating in the J3 quest rewards the contributor with 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP, supporting the healthy redistribution of purchasing power as the server initiates its internal narrative economy. This incentive structure is vital for encouraging the ''Creator'' role (Yellow alignment) to build the symbolic assets that will empower the community. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, J3 is the coordinate where club traditions are formally transformed into digital monuments, ensuring continuity across generations. Once the community reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, these ''Chantier Légende'' memos will be the primary data ingested by ROM, the local RAG engine. ROM will then act as a mythological guide, helping future users navigate the symbolic depth of the node. Ultimately, J3 transforms abstract myths into a permanent, structural reality that secures the node’s cultural integrity for the decade ahead. Done. Yes. Finalized. Now. Perfect. Every single memory here is a brick in our future. Yes.', 'This quest establishes the formal mythological construction site at coordinate J3, where the forom''s sovereign deep lore and symbolic assets are developed and archived.');
