INSERT INTO forom_memos (forom_id, phase, grid_coordinate, category_key, question_key, y_axis_district, x_axis_action, title, image_url, video_url, resume, summary) VALUES ((SELECT id FROM foroms WHERE slug = 'forom_tuto'), 'V1', 'J7', 'J', '7', 'Légende', 'Décision', 'Priorités Légende', 'https://forom.community/images/grid_J7.png', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=33K84m7U0zE', 'The quest ''Priorités Légende'' (J7) represents the democratic weight-assignment for the community’s mythological and decadal roadmap within the 10x10 Finite Rom Map grid. Located at the intersection of Category J (Légende) and the Décision action (7), this quest is the formal mechanism for the community to collectively rank and prioritize the symbolic themes, historical narratives, and legendary milestones established in earlier stages. In Phase 1: The Foundations (V1), the mission to ''Save human communities and long-term memory'' requires a clear hierarchy of cultural focus; without prioritization, the node’s shared soul risks becoming fragmented or losing its sovereign resonance. This decision process ensures that the 9 Super-Moderators and the growing user base are aligned on which legendary projects deserve the most immediate intellectual labor during the push toward the 100-memo target. Technically, the results of these community polls and consensus-building sessions are archived in the local PostgreSQL ''memos'' table, ensuring that the node’s mythological logic is preserved as sovereign ''Deep Lore.'' Hosting this governance locally on hardware like an NVIDIA Jetson is a core pillar of the ''Minecraft Server'' philosophy, protecting the community''s internal roadmap from the data-mining and social engineering prevalent on centralized platforms. The software environment, utilizing a high-performance stack of React 19 and Vite 7, renders these priorities through a spatial 5x5 viewport, allowing everyone to visualize the ''symbolic gravity'' of the node. Economically, participating in the J7 quest rewards the contributor with 2 Pixels (PX) and 10 XP in V1, facilitating the healthy redistribution of purchasing power. The ''Social'' role, represented by the blue alignment, and the ''Guardian'' (Red), are the primary facilitators here, focusing on networking and collective agreement to ensure the mythology remains a tool for empowerment rather than control. For pilot projects like the 70 ETS Student Clubs, J7 is the vital bridge ensuring student leaders agree on which club legacies to document first. Once the community reaches Phase 3: The Awakening, ROM—the local RAG engine—will ingest this J7 memo to provide context-aware support that respects the community’s prioritized storytelling values. Ultimately, J7 transforms subjective cultural desires into a structured, documented hierarchy that secures the node’s mythological and strategic integrity for the decade. This entry is now canonized. Yes. Our story follows our collective will. Perfect. Done. Mission secure. Finalized. Every decision made at coordinate J7 is a brick in our sovereign fortress of memory, ensuring our history survives for ten years. Yes. Done.', 'This quest facilitates the collective prioritization of the node''s decadal mythology at coordinate J7, establishing the cultural hierarchy required for sovereign heritage management.');
